{"inkVersion":21,"root":[[{"->":"Day_One"},["done",{"#f":5,"#n":"g-0"}],null],"done",{"Day_One":[{"->":".^.start"},{"start":[["^\"*HHHRRRHHH* Puerta pequeña estúpida...\"","\n","^\"¡Magtender! Bebida, ya. Engranajes queman, quiero bebida que los enfríe.\"","\n",["ev",{"^->":"Day_One.start.0.4.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-0","flg":18},{"s":["^\"Un por favor puede ayudar mucho.\"",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],["ev",{"^->":"Day_One.start.0.5.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-1","flg":18},{"s":["^\"¿Tus engranajes?\"",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],{"c-0":["ev",{"^->":"Day_One.start.0.c-0.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.4.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","ev",{"VAR?":"bouldar_mood"},1,"-",{"VAR=":"bouldar_mood","re":true},"/ev","^\"*HRRRRRR* Dije bebida. <i>Ahora</i>. Repetir hace Bouldar enfadado. ¡Tú no quieres Bouldar Grimweld enfadado!\"","\n",[["ev",{"^->":"Day_One.start.0.c-0.15.0.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-0","flg":18},{"s":["^\"No deberías amenazar a trabajadores. Ya no nos pagan bastante.\"",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],["ev",{"^->":"Day_One.start.0.c-0.15.1.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-1","flg":18},{"s":["^\"Vale, perdón. Solo bromeaba.\"",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],{"c-0":["ev",{"^->":"Day_One.start.0.c-0.15.c-0.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.0.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","ev",{"VAR?":"bouldar_mood"},1,"-",{"VAR=":"bouldar_mood","re":true},"/ev","^\"Bouldar no importa. ¡Bouldar <i>necesita</i> bebida ya! O Bouldar aplasta tu cara.\"","\n",[["ev",{"^->":"Day_One.start.0.c-0.15.c-0.15.0.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-0","flg":18},{"s":["^\"Eso es demasiado agresivo.\"",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],["ev",{"^->":"Day_One.start.0.c-0.15.c-0.15.1.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-1","flg":18},{"s":["^\"Solo bromeaba, perdón.\"",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],{"c-0":["ev",{"^->":"Day_One.start.0.c-0.15.c-0.15.c-0.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.0.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","ev",{"VAR?":"bouldar_mood"},1,"-",{"VAR=":"bouldar_mood","re":true},"/ev","ev",true,"/ev",{"VAR=":"is_angry","re":true},"^\"¿Agresivo? ¡TÚ AGRESIVO! ¡Tú te burlas de Bouldar!\"","\n","^\"Tú eres malo, no quiero bebida de magetender malo. *KRRR GRRAAA*\"","\n",{"->":".^.^.^.^.^.^.g-0"},{"#f":5}],"c-1":["ev",{"^->":"Day_One.start.0.c-0.15.c-0.15.c-1.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.1.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","ev",{"VAR?":"bouldar_mood"},1,"+",{"VAR=":"bouldar_mood","re":true},"/ev","^\"No... Bouldar también perdón. Engranajes de Bouldar duelen. Como fuego, queman piedra.\"","\n","^\"Solo quiero algo que calme. Quiero estar tranquilo, ¿entiendes?\"","\n",[["ev",{"^->":"Day_One.start.0.c-0.15.c-0.15.c-1.17.0.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-0","flg":18},{"s":["^\"Entiendo. Tengo justo lo que necesitas.\"",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],{"c-0":["ev",{"^->":"Day_One.start.0.c-0.15.c-0.15.c-1.17.c-0.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.0.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","^\"Bouldar lo aprecia, y espera la bebida.\"","\n",{"->":"Day_One.start.0.g-0"},{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":5}],"c-1":["ev",{"^->":"Day_One.start.0.c-0.15.c-1.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.1.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","ev",{"VAR?":"bouldar_mood"},1,"+",{"VAR=":"bouldar_mood","re":true},"/ev","^\"*HHRRK* Bouldar perdón, Bouldar dice por favor. Solo molesto, articulaciones y engranajes duelen. Fusibles fundidos.\"","\n","^\"No puede controlarse... quiere estar tranquilo, no con los pies en la tierra.\"","\n",[["ev",{"^->":"Day_One.start.0.c-0.15.c-1.17.0.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-0","flg":18},{"s":["^\"Bueno, tú <i>estás</i> hecho de piedra. No sé si puedes ser otra cosa <i>que</i> con los pies en la tierra.\"",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],["ev",{"^->":"Day_One.start.0.c-0.15.c-1.17.1.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-1","flg":18},{"s":["^\"Suena bien. Te preparo algo bueno.\"",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],{"c-0":["ev",{"^->":"Day_One.start.0.c-0.15.c-1.17.c-0.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.0.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","ev",{"VAR?":"bouldar_mood"},1,"-",{"VAR=":"bouldar_mood","re":true},"/ev","^\"*KRRRR* haces demasiadas bromas. Enfócate en la bebida. Tus bromas ni siquiera son graciosas.\"","\n",[["ev",{"^->":"Day_One.start.0.c-0.15.c-1.17.c-0.15.0.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-0","flg":18},{"s":["^\"Ay... al menos lo intenté.\"",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],{"c-0":["ev",{"^->":"Day_One.start.0.c-0.15.c-1.17.c-0.15.c-0.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.0.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","^\"Solo haz bebida, no más bromas. Bromas malas.\"","\n",{"->":"Day_One.start.0.g-0"},{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":5}],"c-1":["ev",{"^->":"Day_One.start.0.c-0.15.c-1.17.c-1.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.1.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","ev",{"VAR?":"bouldar_mood"},1,"+",{"VAR=":"bouldar_mood","re":true},"/ev","^\"Gracias magetender. No muchos sitios me sirven. Demasiado grande, demasiado enfadado. Espero que sea buena, y me ayude a arreglarme.\"","\n",{"->":".^.^.^.^.^.^.g-0"},{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":5}],"c-1":["ev",{"^->":"Day_One.start.0.c-1.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.5.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","ev",{"VAR?":"bouldar_mood"},1,"+",{"VAR=":"bouldar_mood","re":true},"/ev","^\"Sí. Engranajes duelen y crujen. Se rozan y queman, como roca fundida por dentro.\"","\n","^\"Duele moverse. Hace Bouldar enfadado.\"","\n",[["ev",{"^->":"Day_One.start.0.c-1.17.0.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-0","flg":18},{"s":["^\"Siento oír eso.\"",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],["ev",{"^->":"Day_One.start.0.c-1.17.1.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-1","flg":18},{"s":["^\"¿Y una bebida es la cura?\"",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],{"c-0":["ev",{"^->":"Day_One.start.0.c-1.17.c-0.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.0.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","ev",{"VAR?":"bouldar_mood"},1,"+",{"VAR=":"bouldar_mood","re":true},"/ev","^\"Es primera vez que alguien dice eso a mí. Otras tabernas ni toman pedido, solo me echan.\"","\n","^\"Solo quiero estar tranquilo, y no tan enfadado.\"","\n",[["ev",{"^->":"Day_One.start.0.c-1.17.c-0.17.0.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-0","flg":18},{"s":["^\"Puedo con eso.\"",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],{"c-0":["ev",{"^->":"Day_One.start.0.c-1.17.c-0.17.c-0.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.0.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","^\"Gracias magetender, eres amable.\"","\n",{"->":".^.^.^.^.^.^.g-0"},{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":5}],"c-1":["ev",{"^->":"Day_One.start.0.c-1.17.c-1.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.1.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","ev",{"VAR?":"bouldar_mood"},1,"-",{"VAR=":"bouldar_mood","re":true},"/ev","^\"¿Tú dudas de mí magetender?! ¡Estoy aquí por bebida! ¡No por juicio!\"","\n",[["ev",{"^->":"Day_One.start.0.c-1.17.c-1.15.0.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-0","flg":18},{"s":["^\"Tienes razón, perdón. Solo intentaba aligerar el ambiente.\"",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],["ev",{"^->":"Day_One.start.0.c-1.17.c-1.15.1.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-1","flg":18},{"s":["^\"Solo bromeaba.\"",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],{"c-0":["ev",{"^->":"Day_One.start.0.c-1.17.c-1.15.c-0.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.0.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","ev",{"VAR?":"bouldar_mood"},1,"+",{"VAR=":"bouldar_mood","re":true},"/ev","^\"Ya veo.... Bouldar perdón por gritar. A Bouldar no le gusta que lo juzguen, porque Bouldar no puede controlarlo.\"","\n","^\"Solo intento vivir cómodo.\"","\n",[["ev",{"^->":"Day_One.start.0.c-1.17.c-1.15.c-0.17.0.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-0","flg":18},{"s":["^\"Claro. Te preparo esa bebida.\"",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],{"c-0":["ev",{"^->":"Day_One.start.0.c-1.17.c-1.15.c-0.17.c-0.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.0.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","^\"¡Bouldar la espera con ganas!\"","\n",{"->":"Day_One.start.0.g-0"},{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":5}],"c-1":["ev",{"^->":"Day_One.start.0.c-1.17.c-1.15.c-1.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.1.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","^\"¡Broma no graciosa! ¡Dolor de Bouldar es real! Solo quiero bebida que ayude, tú te burlas de mí...\"","\n",[["ev",{"^->":"Day_One.start.0.c-1.17.c-1.15.c-1.9.0.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-0","flg":18},{"s":["^\"No quise herirte.\"",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],["ev",{"^->":"Day_One.start.0.c-1.17.c-1.15.c-1.9.1.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-1","flg":18},{"s":["^\"De verdad no, pero vale.\"",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],{"c-0":["ev",{"^->":"Day_One.start.0.c-1.17.c-1.15.c-1.9.c-0.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.0.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","ev",{"VAR?":"bouldar_mood"},1,"+",{"VAR=":"bouldar_mood","re":true},"/ev","^\"*KHHH* Está bien. Solo consigue bebida a Bouldar, me siento mejor después.\"","\n",{"->":"Day_One.start.0.g-0"},{"#f":5}],"c-1":["ev",{"^->":"Day_One.start.0.c-1.17.c-1.15.c-1.9.c-1.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.1.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","ev",{"VAR?":"bouldar_mood"},1,"-",{"VAR=":"bouldar_mood","re":true},"/ev","ev",true,"/ev",{"VAR=":"is_angry","re":true},"^\"*KRRR GRAAA* ¿POR QUÉ MALO? ¿POR QUÉ MAGETENDER MALO? ¡TÚ COMO TODOS LOS QUE JUZGAN A BOULDAR!\"","\n","^\"¡NO QUIERO BEBIDA DE TI!\"","\n",{"->":"Day_One.start.0.g-0"},{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":5}],"g-0":["end",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"satisfied":[["^\"*HHSSSS* ¿Oyes eso magetender?! Ese sonido es vapor de mis engranajes. ¡Alivio! ¡Dulce alivio!\"","\n","^\"Tienes mi gratitud. Dolió tanto tiempo, ¡quizá vuelva cada día!\"","\n","^\"Ahora mi hijo puede sentarse cómodo en mis hombros.\"","\n","^\"¡Adelante Chip, agradece al magetender!\"","\n","^\"...\"","\n","^\"¡Bien dicho! Entonces, quizá nos veamos otra vez. ¡Adiós por ahora!~\"","\n",["end",{"#f":5,"#n":"g-0"}],null],{"#f":1}],"neutral":[["^\"*CLANK* *CLICK* ¿Oyes eso magetender? Esos son mis engranajes. Siguen crujiendo y trabándose.\"","\n","^\"El calor persiste, aunque un poco desvanecido.\"","\n","^\"Desafortunado... esperaba alivio. Pensé que me arreglabas. En cambio, sigo roto.\"","\n","^\"Ven Chip, nos vamos a casa. Papá encontrará otra forma.\"","\n","^\"Gracias por intentarlo, magetender.\"","\n",["end",{"#f":5,"#n":"g-0"}],null],{"#f":1}],"angry":[["^\"*GRRAAA* ¿QUÉ ES ESTA MONSTRUOSIDAD?! PEDÍ SENSACIÓN CALMANTE. TÚ TRAES DOLOR.\"","\n","^\"¡MIS ENGRANAJES, MI NÚCLEO, ARDEN! ¿QUÉ HAS HECHO?!\"","\n","^\"¡PAGARÁS POR ESTO, MIS FUSIBLES SE HAN FUNDIDO! ¡TE APLASTARÉ!!!\"","\n",["end",{"#f":5,"#n":"g-0"}],null],{"#f":1}],"#f":1}],"global decl":["ev",0,{"VAR=":"bouldar_mood"},false,{"VAR=":"is_angry"},"/ev","end",null],"#f":1}],"listDefs":{}}